20
00:02:46,170 --> 00:02:48,010
[Previous Episode]
I’m back.

21
00:02:48,010 --> 00:02:50,210
You looked fine.

22
00:02:50,530 --> 00:02:54,210
It seems that there’s
something important for me to do.

23
00:02:54,290 --> 00:02:55,170
I get it.

24
00:02:55,210 --> 00:02:59,490
Tang San, can’t you let go of these resentments?

25
00:02:59,610 --> 00:03:02,010
Someone is waiting for
my rescue in another place.

26
00:03:02,490 --> 00:03:04,290
<i>Xiao Wu, I’m coming.</i>

27
00:03:07,450 --> 00:03:08,890
It’s you again.

28
00:03:08,930 --> 00:03:12,090
I, Meng Shu has been a soul master for years.

29
00:03:12,090 --> 00:03:14,370
I’m not an unreasonable person.

30
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:17,210
I’ll give you two options.

31
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:24,350
[Soul Land]
[Episode 26]

32
00:03:30,890 --> 00:03:33,410
<i>Although Godly Zhuge Crossbow
can’t injure the two of you,</i>

33
00:03:34,290 --> 00:03:37,490
<i>Meng Yi Ran can’t withstand it. If you go too far,</i>

34
00:03:38,050 --> 00:03:40,970
<i>then don’t blame me for using
your granddaughter as a shield.</i>

35
00:03:40,970 --> 00:03:42,410
Appreciate for more details.

36
00:03:42,410 --> 00:03:47,370
The first option is to join my family.

37
00:03:47,370 --> 00:03:48,890
Join your family?

38
00:03:51,690 --> 00:03:52,410
Yes.

39
00:03:53,610 --> 00:03:56,250
If you become one of my family,

40
00:03:56,370 --> 00:03:59,490
either killing Yi Ran’s hunted soul beast

41
00:03:59,650 --> 00:04:02,410
or wasting the soul ring of
Human Faced Demon Spider

42
00:04:02,930 --> 00:04:06,130
I’ll just let go of them.

43
00:04:11,290 --> 00:04:13,810
<i>Once a soul master joins into a family,</i>

44
00:04:14,210 --> 00:04:17,250
<i>one can never betray it
and is controlled by the family.</i>

45
00:04:17,850 --> 00:04:20,370
Sorry, Senior. I’m used to freedom.

46
00:04:20,850 --> 00:04:21,970
I dislike being constrained.

47
00:04:23,250 --> 00:04:26,490
<i>It’s a great offer for you.
How dare you turn it down.</i>

48
00:04:26,810 --> 00:04:29,890
I’m sorry for obstructing your granddaughter
to obtain the soul ring.

49
00:04:30,330 --> 00:04:31,410
But, you’re wrong for one thing.

50
00:04:32,410 --> 00:04:36,810
If you don’t appear, I must have
absorbed the soul ring of it.

51
00:04:37,170 --> 00:04:38,210
It’ll not be wasted.

52
00:04:38,490 --> 00:04:39,370
What?

53
00:04:43,850 --> 00:04:47,690
You should know that without my permission,

54
00:04:47,810 --> 00:04:51,690
you can’t absorb the Human Faced Demon Spider.

55
00:04:51,930 --> 00:04:55,170
If so, this great soul ring will be wasted.

56
00:04:56,210 --> 00:05:00,810
However, if you join us,
you can absorb the soul ring,

57
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:03,490
and I’ll protect you personally.

58
00:05:03,850 --> 00:05:07,250
Otherwise, even it’s wasted,

59
00:05:07,690 --> 00:05:09,970
we won’t give it to you either.

60
00:05:11,090 --> 00:05:12,090
How about the second option?

61
00:05:12,490 --> 00:05:18,010
Leave an arm as compensation
to my granddaughter.

62
00:05:27,410 --> 00:05:30,090
I can join your family,

63
00:05:33,290 --> 00:05:36,290
if you can fulfill my request.

64
00:05:36,850 --> 00:05:40,610
What makes you qualified to bargain with me?

65
00:05:41,570 --> 00:05:44,410
What is it? Say it.

66
00:05:45,690 --> 00:05:50,010
We met a powerful soul beast before.
It has caught my friend.

67
00:05:52,170 --> 00:05:55,290
If you can help rescue my friend

68
00:05:56,250 --> 00:05:58,610
or take revenge for her,

69
00:06:00,090 --> 00:06:02,610
I promise that I’ll join your family.

70
00:06:03,490 --> 00:06:05,810
Only to hunt a soul beast?

71
00:06:06,530 --> 00:06:09,650
Aren’t you together with Zhao Wu Ji?

72
00:06:10,250 --> 00:06:12,890
Can’t he fight against the soul beast?

73
00:06:15,490 --> 00:06:19,490
If Zhao Wu Ji can’t, it doesn’t mean that I can’t.

74
00:06:20,090 --> 00:06:23,690
With our Fusion Skill,

75
00:06:23,690 --> 00:06:29,290
there are few soul beasts in this Star Dou Forest
which can compete with us.

76
00:06:29,370 --> 00:06:34,010
Tang San, what kind of soul beast is it?

77
00:06:34,010 --> 00:06:36,970
It’s a Titan Giant Ape, above Decade Millennium.

78
00:06:37,170 --> 00:06:38,730
Titan Giant Ape?

79
00:06:45,170 --> 00:06:46,410
We can’t make it.

80
00:06:46,680 --> 00:06:50,490
With your abilities,
can’t you fight the Titan Giant Ape?

81
00:06:50,670 --> 00:06:51,490
You know nothing.

82
00:06:51,970 --> 00:06:55,970
Titan Giant Ape is an ancient
peak-level soul beast.

83
00:06:56,290 --> 00:07:01,570
Not to mention us, even the
Grand Soul Land Master might not beat it.

84
00:07:02,610 --> 00:07:07,810
As far as I know, there’s only
one Titan Giant Ape here.

85
00:07:08,090 --> 00:07:13,610
It is at least 60,000 years old.
A real overlord of the forest.

86
00:07:14,290 --> 00:07:18,330
Moreover, it has a more terrifying brother.

87
00:07:19,050 --> 00:07:24,090
Unless all Grand Soul Land Masters
of two empires gather,

88
00:07:24,850 --> 00:07:28,930
otherwise, no one dares to hunt them.

89
00:07:30,290 --> 00:07:34,890
Unexpectedly, Titan Giant Ape
appeared in forest periphery.

90
00:07:35,110 --> 00:07:37,490
This is not a good omen.

91
00:07:38,570 --> 00:07:40,770
Luckily, it doesn’t initiate a killing feast.

92
00:07:41,450 --> 00:07:46,690
If not, Tang San can’t stay alive until now.

93
00:07:47,890 --> 00:07:48,690
My old man,

94
00:07:48,690 --> 00:07:49,410
Emm.

95
00:07:49,410 --> 00:07:51,410
We should leave here quickly.

96
00:07:51,970 --> 00:07:52,770
Has Xiao Wu...

97
00:07:53,450 --> 00:07:55,250
No. That won’t happen.

98
00:07:55,970 --> 00:07:57,130
Surely there must be a way.

99
00:07:57,650 --> 00:07:58,330
Tang San.

100
00:08:00,170 --> 00:08:03,890
Are you making fun of me with a Titan Giant Ape?

101
00:08:04,290 --> 00:08:08,250
Don’t waste my time.
Tell me about your decision!

102
00:08:11,610 --> 00:08:13,450
You can’t fulfill my wish,

103
00:08:13,850 --> 00:08:15,610
so I won’t join your family.

104
00:08:15,690 --> 00:08:18,090
If you want my arm, take it yourself.

105
00:08:18,170 --> 00:08:20,930
Ha.

106
00:08:24,170 --> 00:08:28,730
Since you want to die, I’ll fulfill your dream.

107
00:08:34,290 --> 00:08:35,850
Senior Dragon Duke, please wait!

108
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:18,890
Senior Dragon Duke, I’m Zhao Wu Ji.

109
00:09:20,370 --> 00:09:22,210
Nice to meet you, Acala.

110
00:09:23,250 --> 00:09:27,090
Stealing Phoenix Tail Crest Serpent first,
then Human Faced Demon Spider.

111
00:09:27,970 --> 00:09:30,890
You’ve taught them well.

112
00:09:31,690 --> 00:09:34,690
Should you give me an explanation?

113
00:09:36,590 --> 00:09:39,490
Senior, there are some misunderstandings.

114
00:09:40,050 --> 00:09:43,290
And I’m a teacher in their school.

115
00:09:43,890 --> 00:09:47,450
Tang San’s master is someone else, not me.

116
00:09:48,090 --> 00:09:48,780
Oh!

117
00:09:49,510 --> 00:09:51,690
Senior, can we talk over there?

118
00:10:10,290 --> 00:10:11,650
Is it real?

119
00:10:27,130 --> 00:10:30,130
Oh, you’re Grandmaster’s disciple!

120
00:10:31,290 --> 00:10:34,930
Unexpectedly, he got a chance
to realize his theory.

121
00:10:36,050 --> 00:10:39,530
Today, I’ll let go of you for the sake of your master.

122
00:10:41,370 --> 00:10:42,090
However,

123
00:10:43,090 --> 00:10:46,850
bear it in mind, if the same things happen again,

124
00:10:47,450 --> 00:10:49,970
I won’t care who your master is.

125
00:10:53,850 --> 00:10:54,810
Thank you, Senior.

126
00:10:55,290 --> 00:10:58,410
<i>Can Master’s fame deter
the Unrivaled Dragon Serpent?</i>

127
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,400
Let’s leave.

128
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:07,890
Grandpa! Grandpa! He has snatched my soul ring
for twice. How can we just let him go?

129
00:11:08,290 --> 00:11:11,010
How do you want to deal with it?

130
00:11:11,490 --> 00:11:16,490
Grandpa is old. I shouldn’t bully the weak.

131
00:11:18,850 --> 00:11:23,610
All right. Since Grandpa doesn’t help,
I’ll do it by myself.

132
00:11:23,720 --> 00:11:24,210
Tang San.

133
00:11:24,330 --> 00:11:24,650
Em.

134
00:11:24,770 --> 00:11:27,130
If you’re a real man, battle with me.

135
00:11:28,330 --> 00:11:31,650
Battle again? Have you forgotten
you had lost to me?

136
00:11:33,170 --> 00:11:34,290
I’ll defeat you this time.

137
00:11:34,690 --> 00:11:37,730
Your soul power is insufficient.
Let’s have a different kind of battle.

138
00:11:39,890 --> 00:11:40,450
How’s the bet?

139
00:11:41,290 --> 00:11:43,410
If you win, you can have
the Human Faced Demon Spider.

140
00:11:43,890 --> 00:11:47,610
If you lose, you’re not allowed to absorb it.

141
00:11:48,460 --> 00:11:48,770
All right.

142
00:11:52,530 --> 00:11:54,290
Wait! This is unfair.

143
00:11:56,210 --> 00:12:00,890
The bet is not fair. If Little San defeats you,
you should do something as well.

144
00:12:01,130 --> 00:12:01,930
What do you want?

145
00:12:02,530 --> 00:12:06,410
Apart from not hindering Little San
to absorb the soul ring, you need to...

146
00:12:09,090 --> 00:12:09,890
What should I do?

147
00:12:13,610 --> 00:12:14,530
Kiss him.

148
00:12:14,930 --> 00:12:15,530
What?

149
00:12:18,290 --> 00:12:18,930
Little Ao!

150
00:12:21,530 --> 00:12:24,170
All right. Let’s carry on.

151
00:12:25,010 --> 00:12:25,730
Grandpa!

152
00:12:26,930 --> 00:12:30,250
Young people should have a little passion.

153
00:12:30,530 --> 00:12:31,690
Let’s begin.

154
00:12:31,810 --> 00:12:32,890
Let’s do it quickly.

155
00:12:33,470 --> 00:12:34,770
How’s the battle go?

156
00:12:54,570 --> 00:12:56,930
[Soul Land]

157
00:13:50,590 --> 00:13:53,550
I’m having 32 soul knives here.
We’ll have 16 respectively.

158
00:13:54,310 --> 00:13:57,030
Later, my grandpa to shake a tree 20 meters away.

159
00:13:57,390 --> 00:14:00,950
We’ll throw the soul knives
at those falling leaves simultaneously.

160
00:14:01,590 --> 00:14:05,590
The one who impales the most leaves will win.
No matter how many leaves are impaled,

161
00:14:06,860 --> 00:14:10,950
the soul knives must be stabbed
on the tree trunk. If not, it won’t be counted.

162
00:14:12,410 --> 00:14:12,830
All right.

163
00:14:17,310 --> 00:14:20,430
Do you need to rest?
I’m not taking advantage of you.

164
00:14:20,950 --> 00:14:22,630
I still have things to do. Let’s start now.

165
00:14:22,630 --> 00:14:23,150
You!

166
00:14:25,590 --> 00:14:29,630
Why do these kids seem confident?

167
00:14:31,670 --> 00:14:33,150
Interesting!

168
00:14:42,230 --> 00:14:43,430
Ready!

169
00:14:56,710 --> 00:14:57,710
Begin.

170
00:15:15,470 --> 00:15:16,390
Didn’t you throw?

171
00:15:16,390 --> 00:15:17,390
I have done it.

172
00:15:17,670 --> 00:15:18,630
What?

173
00:15:18,800 --> 00:15:24,110
It’s such a magical moment! Yi Ran...

174
00:15:24,150 --> 00:15:26,710
[Fifteen seconds ago]

175
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:53,750
Yi Ran, you lost!

176
00:15:55,950 --> 00:15:59,270
It’s unnecessary to see the result! Let’s leave.

177
00:15:59,390 --> 00:16:00,750
No, I don’t believe it.

178
00:16:07,160 --> 00:16:09,110
My girl, admit your failure!

179
00:16:09,750 --> 00:16:12,270
Even I can’t perform Tang San’s technique,

180
00:16:12,540 --> 00:16:17,950
16 soul knives were thrown simultaneously
and stabbed on the tree with only one sound.

181
00:16:18,670 --> 00:16:21,470
Each knife has ten leaves on it.

182
00:16:22,130 --> 00:16:26,030
Besides, he was not facing the tree.

183
00:16:26,030 --> 00:16:27,870
He didn’t use his eye at all.

184
00:16:28,630 --> 00:16:33,310
It’s such a magical technique.

185
00:16:49,070 --> 00:16:49,550
Miss Meng,

186
00:16:50,630 --> 00:16:51,230
your soul knife.

187
00:16:53,990 --> 00:16:56,350
Are you here to tease me?

188
00:16:57,430 --> 00:16:57,950
I don’t.

189
00:17:00,350 --> 00:17:01,270
Then, why are you here?

190
00:17:01,950 --> 00:17:03,630
You don’t need to be sad about your failure.

191
00:17:05,710 --> 00:17:06,550
I’ve been

192
00:17:08,350 --> 00:17:10,230
practicing hidden weapons for nine years.

193
00:17:13,470 --> 00:17:15,870
Nine years? Hidden weapon?

194
00:17:16,350 --> 00:17:17,830
Yes. Nine years.

195
00:17:19,150 --> 00:17:21,390
No. I’m asking you what the hidden weapon is.

196
00:17:23,390 --> 00:17:25,950
Hidden weapon means the weapon to use in secret.

197
00:17:28,830 --> 00:17:30,870
The weapon to use in secret?

198
00:17:35,070 --> 00:17:35,950
What is this?

199
00:17:36,030 --> 00:17:38,310
This is Bone Piercing Needle,
with powerful penetration.

200
00:17:38,950 --> 00:17:40,950
It’s 20% lighter than your knife.

201
00:17:42,150 --> 00:17:43,350
It’s convenient to carry it.

202
00:17:45,330 --> 00:17:46,390
What do you mean?

203
00:17:46,930 --> 00:17:47,390
Gift it to you.

204
00:17:48,070 --> 00:17:48,990
To me?

205
00:17:56,510 --> 00:17:58,910
It should be more suitable that the knife for you.

206
00:17:59,710 --> 00:18:03,790
If you’re willing to, I can tell you
the practice method.

207
00:18:04,810 --> 00:18:06,710
It should be better than your technique now.

208
00:18:07,350 --> 00:18:09,630
What? You want to teach me?

209
00:18:10,310 --> 00:18:12,150
Yes, are you willing to learn?

210
00:18:14,190 --> 00:18:15,030
Can I?

211
00:18:15,860 --> 00:18:16,300
Of course!

212
00:18:17,430 --> 00:18:21,310
Just now, I could perform it precisely
without using my eyes.

213
00:18:21,550 --> 00:18:23,670
It’s the basic technique of using hidden weapons.

214
00:18:25,510 --> 00:18:26,990
It’s known as sound track identification.

215
00:18:28,430 --> 00:18:31,310
Identifying the location
of the target through sound.

216
00:18:31,940 --> 00:18:34,630
There’s no blind zone
when the hidden weapon is shot.

217
00:18:35,050 --> 00:18:36,230
It’s great concealed as well.

218
00:18:56,350 --> 00:18:58,030
I won’t say thanks to you.

219
00:18:59,350 --> 00:19:02,990
I don’t expect it. Just take it as
a compensation for snatching you twice.

220
00:19:14,990 --> 00:19:18,070
This is the bet. Bet is bet. I don’t break it.

221
00:19:18,230 --> 00:19:19,710
Please don’t think much.

222
00:19:36,110 --> 00:19:37,390
Little San, are you feeling good?

223
00:19:43,150 --> 00:19:45,350
Give me one more recovery sausage.

224
00:19:46,830 --> 00:19:50,470
Xiao Wu’s life is uncertain. No more delay.
I’m sorry to bother all of you.

225
00:19:52,130 --> 00:19:53,670
Are you sure not to rest first?

226
00:19:54,350 --> 00:19:56,910
No. Teacher Zhao, please help me.

227
00:20:06,070 --> 00:20:11,670
<i>What a strong soul power wave!
How old is this Human Faced Demon Spider?</i>

228
00:20:25,750 --> 00:20:28,430
Teacher Zhao. This...

229
00:20:29,430 --> 00:20:33,590
Little San might can’t bear this Human Face Demon Spider.

230
00:20:34,630 --> 00:20:37,270
There’s a great gap in their power. It’s vicious.

231
00:20:37,990 --> 00:20:40,670
Little San is more likely going through
a life-or-death challenge.

232
00:20:53,230 --> 00:20:57,390
Grandmaster, join us. Several students are
celebrating their breakthrough.

233
00:21:06,230 --> 00:21:08,830
<i>Xiao Gang, will you be back?</i>

234
00:21:48,790 --> 00:21:53,150
<i>Martial Soul Hall, I’m back!</i>

